WEBVTT

00:00:03.120 --> 00:00:08.000
Mixed reality laboratory is the
place to be for visionaries.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:13.030
Based on a 3D model,
we build a Virtual Reality

00:00:13.030 --> 00:00:19.210
where testing, experiencing and educating
becomes possible in a fun and immersive way.

00:00:19.210 --> 00:00:26.140
Working in the virtual laboratory is
cost effective and it also saves time.

00:00:26.140 --> 00:00:33.180
It makes it easy to test and do
corrections already in the design phase,

00:00:33.180 --> 00:00:40.200
to take care of work safety and
operate future concepts remotely.

00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:45.130
As the pace of research and
development is speeding up,

00:00:45.130 --> 00:00:50.180
VR solutions help bring products to
the market faster than ever before.

00:00:50.180 --> 00:00:55.190
The virtual laboratory is the ultimate design
and testing ground for future innovations.
